    <Heading>
      Tips and Tricks
    </Heading>
    <List>
      <ListItem>To analyze live allocations at an instant, give a
      delay during testing to easily identify that instant in
      spacetrace graphs.</ListItem>
      <ListItem>Use the options to narrow down as much on the
      allocations of interest</ListItem>
      <ListItem>Clicking on linenumber displayed will take you to the
      source code directly.</ListItem>
      <ListItem>Stack traces that differ anywhere wont get merged. So
      it might get difficult to know how much was allocated at a
      given point in code or by a module. Use the restrict callsite to matching text
      in options to narrow down
      </ListItem>
    </List>
